* HTTP Webhooks &\nADF Monitoring
** HTTP Webhooks
***_ Flexible custom integrations
***_ JSON payload sent on event
***_ Control message structure
** Webhook Payload Contains
***_ event_type
***_ workspace_id
***_ run_id, job_id, job_name
** Azure Data Factory Integration
***_ Visual pipeline monitoring
***_ Track pipeline & activity status
***_ Create metric-based alerts
** ADF Alert Metrics
***_ Pipeline run status
***_ Activity run counts
***_ Integration Runtime utilization
** Combined Approach
***_ Databricks: job-level events
***_ ADF: orchestration-level metrics
